author: Taegan Goddard
title: Clinton Super PAC Will Run Benghazi Ad
text:
Clinton Super PAC Will Run Benghazi Ad October 19, 2015 By Taegan Goddard 0 Comments 
The super PAC supporting Hillary Clinton “will advertise on television for the first time in the 2016 presidential campaign, running an ad for two days in the first four early nominating states before her congressional testimony Thursday on the 2012 attacks in Benghazi, Libya,” the New York Times reports. 
“The ad has not been released. But the ad buy, expected to cost six figures, will run on cable networks in New Hampshire, Iowa, Nevada and South Carolina.” Related Posts Never miss a Political Wire post Your email address: * Please enter all required fields Correct invalid entries
